Package com.example.soroban.model

Class Notification

java.lang.Object
com.example.soroban.model.Notification
public class Notification extends Object
Represents a notification associated with an event and user. Stores notification title, message, and associated metadata. References: ChatGPT, StackOverflow, GeeksForGeeks
